{"tid":1683331,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"希望大家加入成為 空投師(2)","createTime":"2019-10-30T15:00:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T15:31:26.000Z","uid":293677,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f45d1ae6a76757761d945402adca597af449a05e","tid":1683331,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:00:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n魔法師有好多<br />\n裝修師都唔少<br />\n但點解無咩人做 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">空投師</span></span>??<br />\n香港明明咁多高樓大廈平台同天橋<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">空投師 唔洗太多裝備<br />\n最緊要係蒙面 同有個袋可以擺到野<br />\n袋住 兩三罐飲品 生果榴槤乜乜乜<br />\n但唔好袋石頭喺身 以防搜身<br />\n亦可以就地取材 垃圾桶 單車 花盤 等等</span><br />\n<br />\n另外<br />\n要識得快速移動 同埋隱藏自己位置同變裝<br />\n見到一群癲狗聚集<br />\n就可以喺高處等待時機 高空奇襲<br />\n掟完即閃 唔好留係現場 化身平民 等待下次機會<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">空投師 就猶如一個狙擊手<br />\n耐性非常好重要<br />\n因為大部分時間都只係 等 同 觀察<br />\n等到時機環境條件成熟 先可以出手<br />\n避免TK記者同手足市民</span><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n最緊要自己熟識既地區<br />\n知道點走<br />\n<br />\n講完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家加入成為 空投師<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1680239\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1680239</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">以上言論 只係講緊打機攻略<br />\n語無倫次 並不代表任何人既立場</span></span>"},{"pid":"f356bcbe18e2392e02563525825430e955da97e6","tid":1683331,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:01:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />歡迎大家建設性討論"},{"pid":"5c8b673576a4f7028c99273a32a33e8aba8719a9","tid":1683331,"uid":68216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:07:44.000Z","msg":"贊成 但要有部署 有計劃先得"},{"pid":"776172b1963369da6648cdcdbfdc533ac3149440","tid":1683331,"uid":278399,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:31:26.000Z","msg":"早排有次喺自己嗰區有咁講過<br />\n一秒就比老母ban咗話好易中到記者<br />\n完"}]}